<template>
      <vue-body-part-selector 
        :selection.sync="selection"
        @click="handleClick"
        :disabled="false"
        :multiple="true"
        body-colour="green"
        selection-colour="yellow"
        :show-parts="{ // won't show head, face and neck
          'head': false,
          'face': false,
          'neck': false,
        }"
      />
</template>

<script>
import VueBodyPartSelector from 'vue-body-part-selector';
export default {
  name: 'App',
  components: {
    VueBodyPartSelector
  }
}
</script>
